<div id="tt86" class="du-bgColor--gray-50 du-margin-top--12 du-padding--4 du-padding-desktopOnly--8">
<h3 class="du-color--coolGray-500 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-letterSpacing--8 du-margin-top--0" id="p55" data-pid="55"><strong>見てみよう</strong></h3>
<div id="tt88" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f7" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=502019300&amp;pub=ijwfq"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1527" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1526" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt89" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p56" data-pid="56">クリスチャンが祝わない祝日にはどんなものがあるでしょうか。</p>
<p id="p57" data-pid="57"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021244/0/0"><strong>「エホバの証人が特定の祝日を祝わないのはなぜですか」</strong>（jw.orgの記事）</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="tt90" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f8" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
<a href="/wol/rslink/r7/lp-j?lang=J&amp;docid=502015120&amp;pub=ijwfq"><img src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1529" data-img-small-src="/ja/wol/mp/r7/lp-j/lff/2021/1528" alt="" width="1200" height="675" class="suppressZoom" /></a>
</figure>
</div>
<div id="tt91" class="dc-column-width--threeQuarters du-margin-children-vertical--0">
<p id="p58" data-pid="58">誕生日を祝うことが神に喜ばれないと言える理由を4つ考えましょう。</p>
<p id="p59" data-pid="59"><a href="/ja/wol/pc/r7/lp-j/1102021244/1/0"><strong>「エホバの証人はなぜ誕生日を祝わないのですか」</strong>（jw.orgの記事）</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div id="tt92" class="dc-columns-desktopOnly du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--gray-100 du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--6 du-padding-top--4">
<div id="f9" class="dc-column-width--oneQuarter du-margin-inlineEnd-desktopOnly--4 du-margin-bottom-mobileOnly--4">
<figure>
